com.absio.crypto.key

Interface IndexedKey

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Key, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractIndexedKey, IndexedECPrivateKey, IndexedECPublicKey

    public interface IndexedKey
extends Key
    Interface for keys that are related to each other. These keys have an active state, an index to help manage them, as well as a specific KeyType (SIGNING or DERIVATION).
